        <div class="body">
            <p>Requests such as this one come in every now and then to the lists.</p>

<p>Several methods are marked final in the action controller: _getParam(), _setParam(), _hasParam(), _getAllParams(), and _forward(). In each case, the underlying functionality is considered essential to basic usage -- i.e., changing it would lead to unexpected results. Using the 'final' visibility operator is the correct way of protecting these from being overridden.</p>

<p>Marking as "Won't Fix".</p>

